01:49:43.340 --> 01:49:56.590
But we know how to compute this
guy in the semiclassical limit,

01:49:56.590 --> 01:49:58.981
which is the string
coupling goes to 0,

01:49:58.981 --> 01:50:00.480
and the other prime
